reviews.text: Not the best or tastiest local restaurant in Kowloon city but the price is definitely one of the cheapest. One set of breakfast costs only 32HKD, includes everything in the picture. Loved the milk tea! Not that many choices on the menu but the atmosphere is comfy and gives off a nostalgic vibe. I came here on a Sunday morning at around 9. Not that many people was inside at that time. Worth a visit if you happen to be around the area.
Good nostalgic feek
service was quick but the instant noodles was overcooked...
good for local style breakfast.
Ok

reviews.text: 價錢屬中下，西餐廳嚟講食譜竟然無意粉？
午飯出品不太好，只是下午茶可以食得下，水吧飲品質素差。
食物○K，但沒有太多 選擇
早餐食物吾錯 唯選擇種類吾多 但價錢比對中肯  沒有即磨 coffee
普通過普通，這裡形冰室開得太濫了。
